                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9979" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0340</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">341 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智能酿造：国台践行企业社会责任之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Intelligent Brewing: Guotai&#39;s Journey in Practicing Corporate Social Responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵斌，平鹤旭，李路路，刘田田，杜秀国</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天津理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贵州国台数智酒业集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智能酿造；国台酒业；企业社会责任；人-机-组织共生；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Intelligent Brewing; Guotai Liquor; Corporate Social Responsibility; Human-Machine-Organization Symbiosis</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着中国经济社会发展，企业伦理、社会责任已经成为企业发展必须面对的课题，只有平衡好企业商业价值与社会价值的关系，才能彰显企业品牌价值，
实现可持续发展。本案例以贵州国台数智酒业集团股份有限公司（以下简称“国台”）艰辛曲折的智能化创新发展历程为主线，讲述了国台在面临多方利益相关
者诉求约束问题时，如何通过打造智能化生产系统，实现商业价值的同时践行企业社会责任；在面临人机冲突时，如何从智能伦理的角度践行对员工的社会责任，
实现人-机-组织共生；在面临消费者对智能酿造的产品质疑时，如何通过智能化手段推动白酒文化传播，最终构建起传统工艺与现代技术融合发展的新型范式。
本案例具体涉及到利益相关者理论、TOE 理论、人-机-组织共生、消费者教育等相关理论知识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abstract: With the development of China&#39;s economy and society, corporate ethics and social responsibility have become issues that enterprises must confront. Only by balancing the relationship between commercial value and social value can enterprises demonstrate their brand value and achieve sustainable development. This case focuses on the arduous and tortuous intelligent innovation and development journey of Guizhou Guotai Digital Intelligence Wine Industry Group Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as &quot;Guotai&quot;), illustrating how Guotai, when faced with the constraints of multiple stakeholders&#39; demands, built an intelligent production system to achieve commercial value while fulfilling its social responsibility; how it addressed the human-machine conflict from the perspective of intelligent ethics to fulfill its social responsibility to employees and achieve symbiosis among humans, machines, and organizations; and how it responded to consumers&#39; doubts about intelligent brewing products by promoting the dissemination of Chinese liquor culture through intelligent means, ultimately establishing a new model of integrated development of traditional craftsmanship and modern technology. This case specifically involves relevant theoretical knowledge such as stakeholders, Technology - Organization - Environment, human-machine-organization symbiosis, and consumer education.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《企业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者；TOE；人-机-组织共生；消费者教育</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
